name: "Collective of Plenty"
title: "Collective of Plenty"
desc: A tribe that prizes strength and muscular physiques, it's said that nearly every member regularly works out.

skills.desc:
When your character prepares a Skill: This character gains 3 Workout.
After your character switches to become the active character: This character gains 2 Workout.
(When Workout stacks reach 3, heal the corresponding character for 1 HP. When Workout stacks reach 5, the corresponding character deals +1 DMG)
